metalign.time

Class TimeSignature

  • java.lang.Object
    • metalign.time.TimeSignature

  • public class TimeSignature
extends java.lang.Object
    A TimeSignature represents some MIDI data's beat structure (time signature). Equality is based only on the numerator and denominator.
    Author:
    Andrew McLeod - 11 Feb, 2015
